LF: legis kidz
6 HOURS LEFT TO APPLY!

Got the fire for policies, debates, and sparking change in the Tamaraw community?

The Legislative Affairs Department is on the lookout for those who are passionate and ready to step up and represent the voice of the students in the 11th FEU Congress.

This is your chance to be at the heart of student legislation, where every motion counts and every idea sparks impact! 

🔗 Apply here:

https://bit.ly/FEUCSOApplicationForm

https://bit.ly/FEUCSOApplicationForm
